{"tid":1575832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭又不認同! 不認同穆迪降香港評級展望","createTime":"2019-09-17T03:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T09:28:50.000Z","uid":14918,"like":44,"dislike":138,"uniUserReply":117,"replies":[{"pid":"ae034d9606dc94f31bff4aea9d0f8a6f8206fd18","tid":1575832,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:47:29.000Z","msg":"《經濟通通訊社１７日專訊》信貸評級機構穆廸將香港評級展望由「穩定」轉為「負面」，<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表示，不認同穆廸的決定，並感到失望，她不同意香港的一國兩制受到削弱或<br />\n與內地進一步融合會模糊一國兩制。不過她認為社會持續不穩會影響國際社會對香港營商環境的<br />\n觀感，需要關注，因此她亦一直強調當前首要之務是恢復法治。<br />\n<br />\n  對於有公務員參與示威活動被捕，林鄭感到非常遺憾，並重申公務員違法一定不被容許，會<br />\n按公務員條例採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n  此外，她又確認政府此早曾接觸國際公關公司，但對方認為香港社會仍未穩定，現時並非適<br />\n當時機重建香港聲譽，但林鄭強調，香港仍有穩健基礎，稍後當局必定會重建香港受損的的聲譽<br />\n。（ｃｌ）（ｚｚ）"},{"pid":"5a629f03e9abfc56877a445c9a8d2ceb684cbace","tid":1575832,"uid":33930,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcb3bbe1d053977aca8403bdbeb5a6b3d80e4b8c","tid":1575832,"uid":29167,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"廢老9upper <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5593e7746a9bff65ff889e283291416623c2cbde","tid":1575832,"uid":242537,"like":152,"dislike":1,"score":151,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:49:23.000Z","msg":"人地文件評級要你認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f90f33e80e940a58699b7b3d7843d